{"tid":1692404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【屯門掃管笏變 「中國城」2】選舉每區都好重要","createTime":"2019-11-04T05:12:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T08:39:47.000Z","uid":99107,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c26994061cf37f5f0f963df702b9a24c7e7e2d07","tid":1692404,"uid":99107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:12:44.000Z","msg":"陳家正，_______。<br />\n<br />\n正仔好有上進心。<br />\n究竟幾想上位，返黎無耐就已經想選村長呢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J4Je07O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ4Je07O.png&h=55a48c9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n二○一九年村代表選舉：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SPpJUs0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSPpJUs0.png&h=79b0440f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然喺落選啦，但唔緊要！做議員，總會有機會上位掛？最近好似有人同「發仔」行得幾埋，叔伯兄弟都陳議員前陳議員後。正仔，你真係以為自己當撚選咗啊？？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但係以第一次嚟講，有咁嘅票數都唔簡單，唔好咁易放過佢</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n鄉黑之子 孽瘤隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://npp.org.hk/npp/article/p/新民黨今天7位成員報名參選2019年區議會選舉\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnpp.org.hk%2Fnpp%2Farticle%2Fp%2F%E6%96%B0%E6%B0%91%E9%BB%A8%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A97%E4%BD%8D%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E5%A0%B1%E5%90%8D%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B82019%E5%B9%B4%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfgwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=b21ef266\" target=\"_blank\">https://npp.org.hk/npp/article/p/新民黨今天7位成員報名參選2019年區議會選舉</a><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">陳家正先生 掃管笏區參選\n陳家正為新民黨本屆最年輕的區選參選人，現年25歲，他為掃管笏的原居民，也是當區居民，見證當區發展，除了原居民，當區持續有新增人口遷入，他希望未來可加強當區的城鄉融合，更好地貢獻社區。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n好叻仔啊，但係你呢排先返黎，係咪真係見證當區發展架，你有無等過小巴呢？ 同埋<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你咁多地咁多屋，仲有2間餐廳同1間地產</span></strong></span>要打理，你係咪真係可以好好服務同貢獻呢個牛屎之地啊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正仔表面資產傳送門</span></span><br />\n餐廳：<br />\nL&rsquo;atlantis<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/r-l-atlantis-屯門-法國菜-fine-dining-r619650\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.openrice.com%2Fzh%2Fhongkong%2Fr-l-atlantis-%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80-%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E8%8F%9C-fine-dining-r619650&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfgwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=0a7d8793\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/r-l-atlantis-屯門-法國菜-fine-dining-r619650</a><br />\n<br />\n正記茶餐廳 （唔知有無露天牌，可以問吓食環）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/r-正記茶餐廳-屯門-港式-r590312\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.openrice.com%2Fzh%2Fhongkong%2Fr-%E6%AD%A3%E8%A8%98%E8%8C%B6%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3-%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80-%E6%B8%AF%E5%BC%8F-r590312&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfgwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=937e3cb9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/r-正記茶餐廳-屯門-港式-r590312</a><br />\n<br />\n地產<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.28hse.com/a1686-1896\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.28hse.com%2Fa1686-1896&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfgwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=93a1bdff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.28hse.com/a1686-1896</a>"},{"pid":"34d060a67407c7340c449ff67abdcf48a2fdf1e9","tid":1692404,"uid":99107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:13:11.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"d9801341ba68e958040ca5307a5ccfec21610e30","tid":1692404,"uid":99107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:13:22.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"a182f5879853b05565cc61ea4939eb3429b452e1","tid":1692404,"uid":99107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:13:32.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"9d1ac6e3f1847f4e55b7900472e95cecf88dff16","tid":1692404,"uid":99107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:13:49.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"a747767fbe2c7938d5